version_description: In this release you’ll see a new way to view wait times and FASTPASS distribution times on attraction detail screens. We also updated account password requirements. Finally, we fixed bugs and enhanced overall app performance.
With this release, we fixed bugs and improved app performance.

Now you can make your Disneyland Resort dining reservations using the app. Reserve a table at a restaurant before your next visit—or even make plans while you’re at the park! You’ll also be able to review upcoming reservations and, if your plans change, cancel them.

We also fixed bugs and enhanced app performance.

With this release, you’ll be able to customize your purchased Disney PhotoPass photos in the app. Crop your vacation photos, add stickers and borders, and save and share your photos, instantly.

We’ve taken steps to improve wait time accuracy—the app will now be using location services and Bluetooth technology to help track how long it’ll take you to get to your experience. We also updated the app to reduce the amount of times you’ll have to log in.

Finally, we fixed bugs and improved overall app performance.

With this release, you’ll be able to maximize your visit with the Disney MaxPass feature! This feature gives you unlimited Disney PhotoPass downloads for the day and allows you to make FASTPASS selections from your device while you’re in the parks. Guests are strongly advised to check the day’s FASTPASS ticket availability and other park details before purchasing the Disney MaxPass feature or using a park ticket with Disney MaxPass. Disney MaxPass is nonrefundable.

With this release, you'll be able to see wait times in near real-time. The app will now display standby wait times as they appear in the park—with little delay. Plus, we added a feature that lets you select which types of notifications you’d like to receive.

With this release, you can now make food and beverage orders at select Disneyland Resort restaurants. Simply select menu items from a participating location, customize your order and pre-pay—right on the app!

Plus, check out our new and improved design. It’s easier than ever to navigate the app and find what you’re looking for. Plan park activities, see vacation info and much more—all from our handy new menu.
